how do I see my billing history from last year

You can view your billing history by logging into your NewsBreak account and navigating to the Billing section. For detailed instructions, you can refer to the Billing Guide here: [Billing Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17821681919757-Billing-Guide). If you need further assistance, feel free to ask!
how do I check dates longer than 8 months

To check billing dates longer than 8 months, you will need to access your billing history through the NewsBreak Ad Manager. If you have trouble finding older records, please contact our support team at adsupport@newsbreak.com for further assistance. You can also refer to the Billing Guide for more information: [Billing Guide](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17821681919757-Billing-Guide).
